comment:
* Contains the configuration of the ad selection process that select a winner from a given list of * ad selection ids. * *

Instances of this class are created by SDKs to be provided as arguments to the {@link * AdSelectionManager#selectAds} methods in {@link AdSelectionManager}.

methods.name: public AdTechIdentifier getSeller()
methods.comment: @return a AdTechIdentifier of the seller, for example "www.example-ssp.com"

methods.name: public List<Long> getAdSelectionIds()
methods.comment:
* @return a list of ad selection ids passed by the SSP to participate in the ad selection from
     *     outcomes process

methods.name: public AdSelectionSignals getSelectionSignals()
methods.comment:
* @return JSON in an {@link AdSelectionSignals} object, fetched from the {@link
     *     AdSelectionFromOutcomesConfig} and consumed by the JS logic fetched from the DSP {@code
     *     SelectionLogicUri}.

methods.name: public Uri getSelectionLogicUri()
methods.comment:
* @return the URI used to retrieve the JS code containing the seller/SSP {@code selectOutcome}
     *     function used during the ad selection
